name: Anubimon
description: Anubismon is a humanoid Digimon with a canine head, green eyes, and two large, feathered, gold wings. It wears a usekh collar around its neck, jeweled bands on its upper arms, and bracelets on its wrist. Its upper body is otherwise unadorned, revealing pale blue fur with dark blue patterns. It has two large hands with claws on them. It wears a sirwal with DigiCode on it that reads デジタルモンスター ( デジタルモンスター , Dejitaru Monsutā ? , lit. "Digital Monster") and winged sandals.
